<TEXT>
London Clubs International, the casino operator, has restructured its board
as part of its attempt to retain its gaming licences. Sir Gordon Booth, a
former senior diplomat and ex-director of Hanson, joins the board as
chairman. The present chairman, Richard Hanson, remains a non-executive
