IMF REVIEW OF BALTIC ECONOMIES 1991
 ------------------------------------------
              Latvia
 ------------------------------------------
GDP                           7.9%.
Consumer prices              +317%.
Real net wages              -21.6%.
 ------------------------------------------
            Lithuania
 ------------------------------------------
